          "text": "Emergent\nNecrotizing Enterocolitis\nVolvulus\nTesticular torsion\nInguinal hernia\nIncarcerated hernia\nTrauma\nPyloric stenosis\nToxic megacolon\nHirschsprung's Disease\nNonemergent\nConstipation\nAcute Gastroenteritis\nColic",
