          "text": "hematuria",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Hematuria"
        },
        {
          "text": "intussusception",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Intussusception"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Supportive\nNSAIDs\nfor pain, may worsen renal disease or GI disease\nConsider\nprednisone\n1mg/kg/day for severe arthralgias, abdominal or scrotal disease\nMay require\nIVIG\nto prevent and treat\nglomerulonephritis",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": [
