        }
      ]
    },
    "Disposition": {
      "text": "Outpatient management for most with rheumatology follow up\nOutpatient renal consult\nRecurrence rate of up to 33%\nIndications for admission include renal failure, significant GI bleeding, and intussusception.\n[6]",
      "subsections": {},
